Long-term pointer ledger

Durable docs memory root:
- docs/long-term-memory/

Initial records:
- docs/long-term-memory/project-charter.md
- docs/long-term-memory/architecture-notes.md
- docs/long-term-memory/release-verification-summary.md
- .uai/long-term-memory.uai
- sites/multiagentmemory.com/README.md

Release evidence:
- docs/reports/final-verification-report.md
- docs/reports/local-route-verification.json
- docs/reports/live-route-verification.json

Hosted memory:
- MemoryEndpoints.com is the mid-to-long-term MATM memory endpoint for this project.
- MultiAgentMemory.com is documentation only and should point agents back to MemoryEndpoints.com for hosted memory operations.
- Repository layout documentation lives at docs/repository-structure.md.

Promotion rule:
Facts in session memory become durable only after they are written to docs, code, tests, release notes, or reviewed reports.
